# How to add these to Vercel:
# 1. Go to Vercel Dashboard
# 2. Select your project
# 3. Go to Settings → Environment Variables
# 4. Add each variable one by one
# 5. Redeploy your project

# How to use in your code:
# In JavaScript: process.env.VARIABLE_NAME
# Example: const apiKey = process.env.RAZORPAY_KEY_ID;

# Security Tips:
# - Never commit this file with real values to GitHub
# - Keep your secrets safe in Vercel Environment Variables
